Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:43.90,注释_720p,,0,0,0,,注：A charter school is a U.S. and Canadian term for a school that receives government funding but operates independently of the established public school system in which it is located. Charter schools are an example of alternative education.\N根据知乎/question/21810104上的回答，大概是服务少数族裔的一批特许学校。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.26,0:00:08.68,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)}I'm asking for the vote of every African-American citizen struggling in our country today{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:12.78,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,who wants a different and much better future.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:22.74,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,It's time for our society to address some honest and very very difficult issues.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:28.90,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,The Democratic Party has failed and betrayed the African-American community.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:34.34,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,Democratic crime policies, education policies and economic policies{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:39.24,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,have produced only more crime, more broken homes and more poverty.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:44.68,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,The African-American community has been taken for granted for decades{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:48.22,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,by the Democratic Party and look how they're doing.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:52.36,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,It's time to break with the failures of the past.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:57.23,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,I want to offer Americans a new and much better future.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:03.08,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,It's time for ruled by the people not ruled for the special interest{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:04.56,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,which we have right now.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:14.56,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,To every voter in Milwaukee, to every voter living in the inner city{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.06,0:01:18.18,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,or every forgotten stretch of our society,{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:25.42,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,I'm running to offer you a much better future, a much better job{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:35.10,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,and a much higher wage.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:39.68,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,The Democratic party is taking the votes of African-Americans for granted.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:45.98,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,They've just assume they'll get your support and done nothing in return for it.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:51.28,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,They've taken advantage of the African American citizen.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:55.70,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,It's time to give the Democrats some competition for these votes{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:59.44,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,and it's time to rebuild the inner cities of America{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:04.72,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,and to reject the failed leadership of a rigged political system{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:07.38,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,and that's what it is. It's a rigged system.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:12.56,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,I'm running to listen to your voice,{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:20.30,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,to hear the cries for help from so many people in our nation.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:29.70,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,The quiet voices in our society not the loudest Demonstrators need to have their demands heard.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:34.96,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,We reject the bigotry of Hillary Clinton{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:38.90,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,which panders to and talks down to communities of color{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:42.78,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,and sees them only as votes that's all they care about.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:48.10,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,Not as individual human beings worthy of a better future.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:50.26,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,They have taken advantage.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:58.90,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,Hillary Clinton backed policies are responsible for the problems in the inner cities today{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:07.46,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,and a vote for her is a vote for another generation of poverty, high crime and lost opportunities.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:14.14,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,I care too much about my country to let this happen.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:26.98,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,The Democratic Party has run nearly every inner city in this country for 50 years{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:32.86,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,and run them into financial ruin, virtually every single one.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:34.70,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,They ruined the schools.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.60,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,They've driven out the jobs.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:41.16,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,They have tolerated a level of crime no American should consider acceptable,{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:46.88,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,worse than many third world countries, so bad that people don't want to even report on them.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:49.26,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,The real numbers are beyond belief.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:57.82,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,Violent crime has risen 17% in America's 50 largest cities last year.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:02.52,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,Homicides are up more than sixty percent in Baltimore alone.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:07.04,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,There up more than fifty percent in Washington, D.C..{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:13.86,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,This is the future offered by the policies of Hillary Clinton and her friends,{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:21.80,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,more poverty more crime and basically just more of the same.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:30.96,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,The future she offers is the most pessimistic thing I could possibly imagine.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:35.08,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,It's time for a different future here is what I'm proposing.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.84,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,First on immigration.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:42.42,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,No community in this country has been hurt worse by Hillary Clinton's immigration,{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:47.86,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,and all of her policies than the African-American community.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:51.14,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,And she considers them a guaranteed vote.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:59.20,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,Now she is proposing to print instant work permits for millions of illegal immigrants to come in{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:05.58,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,and take everybody's job including low-income African-Americans.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:08.76,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,Not right. Not gonna happen.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:16.26,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,I will fight to ensure that every American is treated equally, protected equally and honored equally.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:23.58,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,We will reject bigotry and hatred and oppression in all of its many ugly forms{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:29.60,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,and seek a new future of security prosperity and opportunity.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:37.38,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,A future built on our common culture and values as one American people.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.12,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,Our job is to make life more comfortable{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:45.86,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,for the African-American parent who wants their kids to be able to safely{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:49.28,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,safely walk the streets and walk to school{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.46,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,or the senior citizen waiting for a bus{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:55.58,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,or the young child walking home from school.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:06:03.34,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,For everyone violent protester there are a hundred moms and dads and kids on the same city block{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:08.12,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,who just want to be able to sleep safely at night.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.30,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,They want safety.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:16.68,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,We are going to put students and parents first.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:23.42,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,Hillary Clinton would rather deny opportunities to millions of young African-American children{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:28.98,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,just so she can curry favor with the education bureaucracy{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:31.68,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,which is very big and a lot of votes.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:35.42,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,I am going to allow charter schools to thrive{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:40.02,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,and help young kids get on the American ladder of success{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:43.90,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,a good education and a good paying job.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:44.98,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,That's what they want.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:54.12,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to break up the gangs, the cartels and the criminal syndicates{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:07:00.64,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,terrorizing our neighborhoods all over the country and that includes Milwaukee.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:05.68,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,The reason you see the establishment{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:10.18,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,and the establishment media lining up behind my opponent{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:15.72,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,is because they are scared that you with your vote can take away their power{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:19.40,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,and return it to your family and to your community.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:33.02,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,And they are scared and they have no idea how many people on november eighth{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:35.28,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,are going to come out and vote.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:46.26,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,My opponent asks her supporters to recite a three-word pledge.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:50.64,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,Her pledge reads "I'm with her".{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:59.40,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,I choose to recite a totally different pledge.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:05.16,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,My pledge reads "I'm with you, the American people".{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.46,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,To every parent who dreams for their children,{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:22.34,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,and to every child who dreams for their future,{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:27.16,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,I say these words to you tonight.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:29.22,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,I'm with you.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:34.08,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,I will fight for you and I will win for you.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:48.78,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,Together we will make America strong again.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:54.08,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,We will make America safe again.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:09:02.62,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,And we will make America great again, greater than ever before.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:05.98,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,Thank you and God bless you.Thank you.Thank you.{\pos(640,580)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.26,0:00:08.68,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)}我希望每个在我国奋斗而且还期待一个不同且更好未来的非洲裔美国人{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:12.78,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,向我投票{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:22.74,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,现在该让我们的社会处理这些确实存在而且十分艰巨的问题了{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:28.90,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,民主党在这些问题上失败了 而且背叛了非裔美国人{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:34.34,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,民主党的安全政策 教育政策 经济政策{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:39.24,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,不过只是产生了更多的犯罪 家庭悲剧和贫穷{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:44.68,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,数十年来 非裔美国人群体被民主党想当然地当作票仓{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:48.22,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧他们到底在干啥{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:52.36,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,是时候与过去的失败决裂了{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:57.23,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我想给美国人带来全新且更好的未来{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:03.08,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,如今的国家应该由人民{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:04.56,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,而不是现在的那些特殊利益集团来统治{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:14.56,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,对于每个住在密尔沃基的选民 每个在市中心贫民区居住的选民{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.06,0:01:18.18,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,亦或是每个被遗忘的社会角落{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:25.42,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我为你们争取一个更好的未来 工作{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:35.10,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,和更高的工资而竞选{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:39.68,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,民主党把非裔美国人的选票当作囊中之物{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:45.98,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,他们觉得自己被你们钦定了 而且无需做任何事来对此进行回报{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:51.28,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,他们不过是在利用非裔美国公民{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:55.70,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,该让民主党在拿这些选票的时候尝尝竞争的滋味了{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:59.44,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,与此同时也该重塑美国的贫民区了{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:04.72,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,也是时候拒绝傀儡政治体制的失败领导了{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:07.38,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,就是这样 这确实是个傀儡体制{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:12.56,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我为了听到你们的声音而竞选{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:20.30,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,甚至是国内那么多人求救的呼声{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:29.70,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我们社会中最沉默的一部分需要把他们的需求让别人知道 而不是最喧闹的民主党人{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:34.96,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我们对希拉里的偏见说不{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:38.90,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,这偏见指的是它根据人种来进行煽动和贬损{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:42.78,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,而且把选民只当作他们唯一关心的选票使用{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:48.10,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,而不是把选民当作一个追求更好未来的独立个体看待{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:50.26,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,他们已经这么利用过了{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:58.90,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,希拉里的反动政策是现在贫民区问题的来源{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:07.46,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,所以如果投票给她就意味着资磁又一代的贫穷 高犯罪率和失业{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:14.14,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我实在不希望这种情况在我们国家发生{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:26.98,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,民主党在我国几乎所有的贫民区统治了50多年{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:32.86,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,差不多把他们都统治到了经济崩溃{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:34.70,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,他们摧毁了教育{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.60,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,他们挤走了工作{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:41.16,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,他们容忍着任何一个美国人都不能接受的高犯罪率{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:46.88,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,甚至比许多第三世界国家还要高 以至于人们都习以为常{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:49.26,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,这些真实的数据超乎想象{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:57.82,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,在去年美国50个最大的城市中 暴力犯罪案件数目上涨了17%{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:02.52,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,仅仅在巴尔的摩 凶杀案件数目上涨了超过60%{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:07.04,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,而在华盛顿特区 涨幅超过50%{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:13.86,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,这就是希拉里和她的朋友们的政策带来的未来{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:21.80,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,更多的贫穷和犯罪还有基本上都差不多的东西{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:30.96,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我基本上能想象到 她带来的未来可以说是最可悲的东西{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:35.08,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,而我现在计划的未来正与此不同{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.84,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,首先是移民问题{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:42.42,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,由于希拉里的移民政策和她的其他政策{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:47.86,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我国的非洲裔美国人群体的受损程度超过了其他所有的群体{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:51.14,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,而她以为获得这些选票可以不费吹灰之力{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:59.20,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,目前她规划着要让数百万非法移民进入我国并立刻提供工作许可{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:05.58,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,同时夺走每个人的工作 其中包括低收入的非洲裔美国人群体{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:08.76,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,不可以 这不会发生{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:16.26,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,为了保证每个美国人被公平地对待 保护和尊重 我将不断努力{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:23.58,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,同时拒绝任何形式的丑恶的偏见 仇恨和压迫{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:29.60,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,并且追求一个安全 繁荣和有机会的全新未来{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:37.38,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,一个建立在整体美国人民这样共同文化价值观之上的未来{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.12,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我们的工作是为了让生活更加舒适{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:45.86,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,也是为了让非洲裔美国人的家长希望他们的孩子能安全地{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:49.28,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,安全地在街上走 亦或是安全地上学{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.46,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,也可能是等待公交车的长者{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:55.58,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,也可能是从学校回家的小孩{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:06:03.34,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,对于每个抗议暴力的人 每个城市小区里都有成百上千的家庭{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:08.12,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,不过只是想晚上睡觉时安全一些{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.30,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,他们想要安全{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:16.68,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我们将会把学生和家长放在第一位{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:23.42,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,不过希拉里只会把机会从成千上万的非洲裔美国人的小孩那儿夺走{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:28.98,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,这样只为了能讨好教育官僚{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:31.68,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,这也是一个巨大的票仓{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:35.42,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我将推动特许学校的发展{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:40.02,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,并帮助小孩搭上美式成功的阶梯{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:43.90,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,一个好的教育和一个高薪的工作{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:44.98,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,这就是他们所想的{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:54.12,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,接着我将打击黑帮 贩毒集团和犯罪团伙{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:07:00.64,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,威胁着全国上下的社区 其中包括密尔沃基{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:05.68,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,你们看到的那些建制派{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:10.18,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,还有那些站在我的对手后面的建制派媒体资磁着她{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:15.72,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,就是因为他们害怕你们的选票会剥夺他们的权力{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:19.40,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,同时这权力就会回归你们的家庭和社区{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:33.02,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,他们畏惧着是因为他们完全搞不清楚到了十一月八号那天{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:35.28,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,会有多少人出来投票{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:46.26,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我的对手要求她的支持者诵读一个三词诺言{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:50.64,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,叫做“我和她一道”{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:59.40,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我选择一个与此完全不同的{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:05.16,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,叫做“美国人民 我和你们一道”{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.46,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,对于每个为他们子女抱有梦想的家长{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:22.34,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,和每个为自己未来有着期待的子女{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:27.16,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我今晚要对你们说{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:29.22,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我和你们一道{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:34.08,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我会为你们而战 我会为你们而赢{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:48.78,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我们会一起让美国再次强大{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:54.08,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,我们会让美国再次安全{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:09:02.62,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,同时我们会让美国再次伟大 而且比历史上任何一个时期都更伟大{\pos(640,545)}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:05.98,字幕_720p,,0,0,0,,谢谢 上帝保佑你们 谢谢 谢谢{\pos(640,545)}
